core:dendroidGuard.description:
{green|Dendroid Guard}

Slow and powerful dendroids bash their opponents with their wooden limbs. Those attacked by dendroids are snared in tangling roots and bound in place until the dendroids move or are killed.

{gold|Special Ability : Binding}
Dendroids' attack causes an enemy to be bound to the ground, unable to move until the stack of dendroids that entangled them moves or perishes, but the effect can also be removed with Dispel or Teleport spells. The visual effect of binding is a bunch of roots appearing from the ground. Anti-Magic doesn't protect units from being bound by this ability.

core:dendroidSoldier.description:
