core:unicorn.description:
{green|Unicorn}
Unicorns and war unicorns have excellent mobility and deliver severe damage with their lancing horn attack.

{gold|Special Ability : Blinding and Aura of magic resistance}
Unicorn's horn attack has a 20% chance of blinding an opponent. Both unicorn units project a magic resistant aura which gives adjacent units a 20% chance to ignore the effects of hostile spells. This aura of resistance also applies to the creature itself.

core:warUnicorn.description:
{green|War Unicorn}
